node.text: Ever wondered how to make COCONUT WHIPPED CREAM🤔? The struggle can be real, but we’re showing you our foolproof methods for PERFECT coconut whip every time😋! We share tips, tricks, and detail exactly what coconut cream brands will set you up for success🥥🥛. Read our STEP-BY-STEP methods via the LINK in our bio! #howto #whippedcream #plantbased #dessert⁠

node.title: How To Make Coconut Whipped Cream

node.text:
Maybe we're crazy for craving soup during summer, but sometimes it just hits right 🥣 Our 1-Pot Tortilla 🌮 Soup is smoky 🔥, savory, spicy 🌶, & SO easy! Just 10 INGREDIENTS & 1 POT required. Top with a little avocado 🥑 and you've got a PERFECT comforting meal to make this week! 🤩⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Find the recipe here: minimalistbaker.com/1-pot-vegan-tortilla-soup/⁠⁠
⁠⁠
#tortillasoup #tacosoup #vegansoup #easyvegandinners #easyveganrecipes⁠⁠
⁠⁠

NEW! Ever tried a Jamocha Shake before? 🥤 Our DECADENT plant-based version is about to rock your world 🤩 Think: creamy coconut milk 🥥 blended with cold brew ☕️, cacao powder 🍫, nutty almond butter 🥜, & a pinch of sea salt 🤌🏻...yeah, you heard that right. 😉 It's chocolatey, rich, & just SO good. // LINK in bio for the full recipe!⁠⁠
⁠⁠
